acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

params.quoteToken: The address of the quote token.

claimFees(address).details: Claims the fees of the specified market. Only the creator of the market can claim the creator fees. Only the staking contract can claim the staking fees.

claimProtocolFees(address).details: Claims the protocol fees of the specified token.

claimReferrerFees(address).details: Claims the referrer fees of the specified token.

createMarketAndToken((uint96,string,stri.details: Creates a new market and token.

returns.baseToken: The address of the base token.

getCreatorMarketAt(address,uint256).details: Returns the market at the specified index created by the specified creator.

returns._0: The address of the market created by the creator at the specified index.

getCreatorMarketsLength(address).details: Returns the number of markets created by the specified creator.

returns._0: The number of markets created by the creator.

getCreatorOf(address).details: Gets the creator of the specified market.

returns._0: The address of the creator of the market.

getFeeSharesOf(address).details: Gets the fee shares of the specified market, which includes the protocol, and staking shares.

getMarket(address,address).details: Gets the market of the specified tokens.

params.tokenA: The address of the first token.
params.tokenB: The address of the second token.

returns._0: A boolean indicating if the first token is the base token
returns._1: The address of the market of the tokens.

getMarketAt(uint256).details: Gets the market at the specified index.

returns._0: The address of the market at the specified index.

getMarketOf(address).details: Gets the market of the specified token.

returns._0: The address of the market of the token.
The address of the protocol fee recipient.

getProtocolFees(address).details: Get the protocol fees of the specified token.

returns._0: The total protocol fees of the token.

getReferrerFeesOf(address,address).details: Returns the referrer fees of the specified token.

returns._0: The total referrer fees of the token.

getReferrerShare().details: Gets the referrer share percentage. The referrer share percentage is the percentage of the protocol fees that will be distributed to the referrer (if any).

getTokenImplementation(uint96).details: Gets the token implementation of the specified token type.

returns._0: The address of the token implementation.

getTokenType(address).details: Gets the token type of the specified token.

returns._0: The token type of the token.

handleProtocolFees(address,address,uint2.details: Handles the fees of the specified token. Must be called by a valid market contract.

params.token: The address of the quote token.

returns._0: bool for gas optimization. This value can be ignored.

initialize(uint16,uint16,address,address.details: Initializer for the TokenMill Factory contract.

params.initialOwner: The address of the initial owner.
params.protocolFeeRecipient: The address of the protocol fee recipient.

isQuoteToken(address).details: Checks if the specified token is a quote token.

returns._0: A boolean indicating if the token is a quote token.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

params.quoteToken: The address of the quote token.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner.

updateCreatorOf(address,address).details: Updates the creator of the specified market.

updateFeeSharesOf(address,uint16,uint16).details: Updates the fee shares of the specified market.

params.protocolFeeRecipient: The address of the protocol fee recipient.

updateTokenImplementation(uint96,address.details: Updates the token implementation of the specified token type.

params.implementation: The address of the token implementation.
